to spare your life.

9
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:17,680
Just leave.

10
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:20,079
You sinful villain!

11
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,710
You'll go to hell and die miserably!

12
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,560
You'll definitely be killed by Duan.

13
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,920
Shaoyi will also take revenge for our Fire Crane Tribe!

14
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,200
Listen.

15
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:31,160
Whether it's this life or next life,

16
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,760
Duan Yu will never be able to defeat me!

17
